48:56.000 --> 48:58.534
<i>Another epidemic
of missing women</i>

48:58.536 --> 49:00.202
<i>is among us in our city.</i>

49:00.204 --> 49:03.306
<i>While police are suspecting
links to organized crime,</i>

49:03.308 --> 49:07.209
<i>some are speculating it could
all be the work of just one man.</i>

49:07.211 --> 49:10.313
<i>The repeated attacks
on escorts and street walkers</i>

49:10.315 --> 49:14.951
<i>have some calling the assailant
the latter-day Jack the Ripper.</i>

49:14.953 --> 49:17.253
<i>In related news,
there is a new development</i>

49:17.255 --> 49:19.422
<i>in the Mary Rollins
disappearance.</i>

49:19.424 --> 49:21.457
<i>Police cannot confirm
a connection,</i>

49:21.459 --> 49:24.560
<i>but they're now trying
to identify a possible suspect</i>

49:24.562 --> 49:27.396
<i>caught on the bar's
parking lot surveillance cam.</i>

49:45.149 --> 49:46.615
Yeah, I got your email.

49:46.617 --> 49:48.751
<i>Yeah, theirs is
few review copies gone out</i>

49:48.753 --> 49:51.454
<i>and there's a few copies
floating around the office.</i>

49:51.456 --> 49:53.539
What are the interns saying?

49:53.540 --> 49:55.623
<i>Well, you know, Mitch, this is...
this is really ambitious.</i>

49:55.626 --> 49:58.160
<i>I think you should be
really proud of yourself.</i>

49:58.162 --> 50:00.229
I am proud.

50:00.230 --> 50:02.297
<i>I just hope you are hard
at work on the next one.</i>

50:02.300 --> 50:05.001
Yeah, I just got pages
flowing out of me.

50:06.304 --> 50:07.770
Any updates, Detective?

50:07.772 --> 50:09.305
None so far, Sir.

50:09.307 --> 50:11.240
I have been keeping
a close eye on him,

50:11.242 --> 50:14.143
but I've got about as close
as I can get without a warrant.

50:14.145 --> 50:16.545
No, remember, we want
to keep this quiet.

50:16.547 --> 50:17.780
He's kind of a big shot in town.

50:17.782 --> 50:19.615
Big shots are my specialty, Sir.

50:19.617 --> 50:22.418
Detective,
we do not want a repeat

50:22.420 --> 50:24.186
of your last investigation.

50:24.188 --> 50:25.688
There won't be, Sir.

50:25.690 --> 50:26.690
Good.

50:27.625 --> 50:30.359
Just play it cool
with Stockridge.

50:30.361 --> 50:32.762
- No more gut feelings.
- Understood.

50:50.148 --> 50:52.181
Yeah, gotcha.

51:08.299 --> 51:09.565
Yeah, I know.

51:13.404 --> 51:14.737
I'm just disappointed.

51:15.640 --> 51:17.306
You can do better than that.

51:17.308 --> 51:20.576
Fuck you, grand old
dork motherfucker.

51:21.446 --> 51:22.611
Piece of shit!

51:31.089 --> 51:32.354
You seem tense.

51:33.191 --> 51:34.457
I hope you're happy

51:34.459 --> 51:37.493
because they're saying what
you've been saying all along.

51:38.296 --> 51:40.229
I'll have to take
your word for it.

51:41.265 --> 51:43.165
I don't get them much.

51:43.167 --> 51:44.767
I tried to do
something different,

51:44.769 --> 51:46.769
something new,
something from here.

51:50.173 --> 51:51.739
But in the end, it was
the same old trick.

51:51.742 --> 51:54.210
What are you telling me for?

51:54.212 --> 51:56.278
Because I don't have
mom to talk to anymore.

51:57.482 --> 51:59.115
She would have made you soft.

52:14.132 --> 52:16.632
I guess I'm just more
of a short story guy, huh?

52:16.634 --> 52:18.200
Aren't you on top of this?

52:18.202 --> 52:20.369
We publicized all we could.

52:21.739 --> 52:24.540
I guess one week here on top,
next week it's a ghost town.

52:27.745 --> 52:28.778
I just don't understand.

52:28.779 --> 52:29.812
- The book's out and...
- And?

52:29.814 --> 52:31.914
Well, you read the reviews.

52:31.916 --> 52:33.716
I just don't get it.
This book has everything.

52:33.718 --> 52:36.485
I know, your blood,
your sweat, your tears.

52:36.487 --> 52:38.888
Is this the
Terrance Williams signing?

52:38.890 --> 52:40.623
No, he was here yesterday.

52:40.625 --> 52:42.558
Oh. Sorry.

52:42.560 --> 52:44.793
- Fucking Terrance.
- Oh, come on, Mitch.

52:44.795 --> 52:47.196
You know the reading
public's fickle.

52:47.198 --> 52:49.565
Maybe they just needed something
different this time around.

52:49.567 --> 52:52.268
- Thanks for your input.
- I'm just trying to be helpful.

52:52.937 --> 52:55.471
Oh, great, hope that
makes you feel better.

53:00.378 --> 53:01.461
<i>Voilá.</i>

53:01.462 --> 53:02.545
It's better be
as good as you say.

53:02.547 --> 53:04.387
You've been rolling it
for half hour.

53:16.527 --> 53:17.527
I love you.

53:24.735 --> 53:27.970
I just don't know what happened.
There was like nobody there.

53:27.972 --> 53:29.538
Well, I'll be honest.

53:30.341 --> 53:31.607
You finished it last night.

53:34.312 --> 53:35.312
Yeah?

53:37.782 --> 53:39.715
I'm your friend, I'm gonna
give it to you straight.

53:39.717 --> 53:40.717
I know.

53:42.620 --> 53:45.221
Something is different
about you, man.

53:45.223 --> 53:47.456
Something's changed.
I don't know what it is.

53:48.426 --> 53:50.392
And maybe you need to stay
with the small stuff.

53:50.394 --> 53:52.034
No one is gonna
fault you for that.

53:52.563 --> 53:54.413
Some people will.

53:54.414 --> 53:56.414
Come on, Mitch, who's
gonna fault you for that?

53:58.369 --> 54:00.402
Nick, what motivates you
to get up in the morning,

54:00.404 --> 54:01.604
go to the office and all that?

54:04.508 --> 54:06.108
If I didn't,
I wouldn't have a job.

54:09.013 --> 54:10.613
I don't know what
you want me to say, man.

54:10.615 --> 54:11.914
I mean, I'm living it up here.

54:11.916 --> 54:13.749
You know, I got a
great middle-class life.

54:13.751 --> 54:17.553
I have a wife who's
way too hot for me.

54:17.555 --> 54:19.755
It's more than we could've
ever dreamed of as kids.

54:20.992 --> 54:23.726
All we had as kids it's Luke
Rousseau beating our faces in

54:23.728 --> 54:25.995
every day for our lunch money.

54:25.997 --> 54:29.565
And if you lost your job,
your career went belly-up,

54:29.567 --> 54:31.734
how would Laura react?

54:32.870 --> 54:35.004
Laura would be
extremely disappointed.

54:35.006 --> 54:36.372
She'd be pissed off for a while.

54:37.608 --> 54:39.808
But Laura doesn't depend
on material things

54:39.810 --> 54:41.410
to make her happy.

54:41.412 --> 54:42.945
Let's say you did
a really good job at work,

54:42.947 --> 54:45.648
and you got a promotion
and a bonus

54:46.484 --> 54:48.784
or whatever, and you were
able to buy a bigger house.

54:50.021 --> 54:51.754
Then, not to say it's bad now,

54:51.756 --> 54:53.716
but your relationship
would be better, right?

54:55.293 --> 54:56.592
Can be worse.
I'll give you that.

54:56.594 --> 54:58.434
Okay, then you see
where I'm coming from.

55:01.365 --> 55:02.898
Here comes the airplane.

55:06.704 --> 55:08.737
Look who's in a good mood.

55:09.607 --> 55:11.907
Yeah, I am.

55:11.909 --> 55:13.409
I finally figured something out.

55:18.783 --> 55:19.915
From now on,

55:20.985 --> 55:23.018
you're gonna like
me for who I am

55:23.854 --> 55:27.022
or you can just
go fuck yourself.

55:28.659 --> 55:29.758
What about you?

55:31.629 --> 55:33.762
Do you like yourself?

55:33.764 --> 55:34.930
I'm gonna give it a try.

55:36.734 --> 55:39.068
You hate yourself, Mitch.

